<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Order Confirmation - F1 Tickets</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #d81b60;
        }
        .order-details {
            background: #fafafa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Dear <%= @order.user.username %>,</h2>
        <p>Thank you for your recent order from <strong>F1 Ticketing</strong>.</p>

        <p><strong>You ordered the following items:</strong></p>
        <<div class="order-details">
            <% @line_items.each do |line_item| %>
                <%= sprintf("%2d x %s %s", line_item.quantity, line_item.ticket.event.name, line_item.ticket.category) %> <br>
            <% end %>
        </div>>

        <p>You will receive an email with your e-tickets in the coming days. Please feel free to reach out if you do not.</p>

        <p>Kind regards,</p>
        <p><strong>F1 Ticketing Team</strong></p>

        <div class="footer">
            &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> F1 Ticketing. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
